text: Tulip Rizwana Siddiq (; born 16 September 1982) is a British Labour Party co- operative politician. She was elected Member of Parliament (MP) for Hampstead and Kilburn at the 2015 general election. Siddiq is Muslim. ==References== ==Other websites== * * *Tulip Siddiq on Huffington Post *Tulip Siddiq on Camden Council Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:British Muslims Category:Politicians from London
